16/08/2021
Hey, How are you?

Well, today is rather good for a Monday morning and I think it's due to my mental fortitude and understanding of how I can make reality mine. Today I woke up with a stark reminder that the world is flawed, that we are all flawed and that I myself might be flawed.

Well thats's deep, what made you feel this way and what part of it do you think affected you?

So my friends gave into their emotions yesterday and let their feelings get the better of their intellect. This was a sight for sore eyes as I had put these niggas on a pedestal and was stunned by their sheer lack of will to overcome an awkward situation. How did it affect me? I think it made me realize the grip emotions have on even the intelligent. Moreover, it made realise I have to kill my will to love and depend on people as these "people" are inherently flawed and acutely unpredictable. Love is going to die in me and I have to do the killing.

Why do you feel killing love is the way forward?

My reality is one thing, my biology is another. Like sickness, love creates a physical/chemical reaction that even the mind has little control over. I do not want to lose a grip on MY existence through falling in love, I do not desire a world where I let a relationship determine my happiness, I do not desire dependence, I desire autonomy, Independence, free from animalistic emotions, free from things that can dictate my reality. If what we see, hear, smell, feel and believe don't matter, why don't we truly live life as we deem fit to the fullest of our capabilities? why don't we go completely out the curb and begin driving on the grass? the grass grows back, we die and all actions lose meaning. Why don't we live? Why don't we live like the world as we know it would factually be gone in a hundred years? Why do we live as if any of it matters?

January 6th 2023

m damn man thanks really that's deep but this is kind of half assed tbh

g oh xDDDDDDDDD nice one xDDDDDDDDDDDDD

m yh man just having a laugh as well

g okay one big question, what exactly are you trying to do

m tbh I'm just tryna accomplish my goals organically and not stress too much about the fine details anymore, I want to do what I need to do and try to do it when I can do it. I am not trying to stress but at the same time I am trying to zero into accomplishing my goals. DOing so last year gave me a big boost and I'm looking forward to continuing in a similar strength. But most of all I am trying to make the best out of my life while I am alive

g well said G, just make sure you check in w yourself and are making the right decisions on a bigger scale. 

m Go on, thanks G! I love you ‚ù§Ô∏è
